quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  6,69,Wa Mā `Alá Al-Ladhīna Yattaqūna Min Ĥisābihim Min Shay'in Wa Lakin Dhikrá La`allahum Yattaqūna
  6,70,Wa Dhari Al-Ladhīna Attakhadhū Dīnahum La`ibāan Wa Lahwan Wa Gharrat/humu Al-Ĥayāatu Ad-Dunyā Wa Dhakkir Bihi 'An Tubsala Nafsun Bimā Kasabat Laysa Lahā Min Dūni Allāhi Wa Līyun Wa Lā Shafī`un Wa 'In Ta`dil Kulla `Adlin Lā Yu'ukhadh Minhā 'Ūlā'ika Al-Ladhīna 'Ubsilū Bimā Kasabū Lahum Sharābun Min Ĥamīmin Wa `Adhābun 'Alīmun Bimā Kānū Yakfurūna
  6,71,Qul 'Anad`ū Min Dūni Allāhi Mā Lā Yanfa`unā Wa Lā Yađurrunā Wa Nuraddu `Alá 'A`qābinā Ba`da 'Idh Hadānā Allāhu Kālladhī Astahwat/hu Ash-Shayāţīnu Fī Al-'Arđi Ĥayrāna Lahu 'Aşĥābun Yad`ūnahu 'Ilá Al-Hudá A'tinā Qul 'Inna Hudá Allāhi Huwa Al-Hudá Wa 'Umirnā Linuslima Lirabbi Al-`Ālamīna
  6,72,Wa 'An 'Aqīmū Aş-Şalāata Wa Attaqūhu Wa Huwa Al-Ladhī 'Ilayhi Tuĥsharūna
  6,73,Wa Huwa Al-Ladhī Khalaqa As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđa Bil-Ĥaqqi Wa Yawma Yaqūlu Kun Fayakūnu Qawluhu Al-Ĥaqqu Wa Lahu Al-Mulku Yawma Yunfakhu Fī Aş-Şūri `Ālimu Al-Ghaybi Wa Ash-Shahādati Wa Huwa Al-Ĥakīmu Al-Khabīr